OL,3,CDad of murdered teen Kiyan Prince is
OL,4,Ctransforming lives 20 years on
OL,6,FMark Prince showed ITV News' Mary
OL,7,FNightingale how he is changing the
OL,8,Flives of young people 20 years after
OL,9,Fhis 15-year-old son Kiyan was fatally
OL,10,Fstabbed while trying to break up a
OL,11,Ffight outside his school.
OL,13,FI first met Mark Prince in 2006, just
OL,14,Fdays after the death of his son.
OL,16,FKiyan had been fatally stabbed while
OL,17,Ftrying to break up a fight outside of
OL,18,Fhis school.JA talented footballer,
OL,19,FKiyan was signed up to Queen's Park
OL,20,FRangers' Youth Academy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
