OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779102176
OL,3,CDad of murdered teen Kiyan Prince is
OL,4,Ctransforming lives 20 years on
OL,6,FIt was hoped he might have a career in
OL,7,Fthe game, if that early promise paid
OL,8,Foff. A boy with a bright future, then.
OL,10,FBut it was not to be.
OL,12,FKiyan Prince was only 15 years old
OL,13,Fwhen he was murdered by another
OL,14,Fteenager.
OL,16,FHis death prompted an outpouring of
OL,17,Fpublic grief. Hundreds of mourners
OL,18,Fleft flowers outside his school in
OL,19,FNorth London.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
