PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779102176
OL,3,CDad of murdered teen Kiyan Prince is
OL,4,Ctransforming lives 20 years on
OL,6,FAt that time, stabbings, particularly
OL,7,Finvolving young black men and boys,
OL,8,Fwere all too often making the
OL,9,Fheadlines. There was talk of an
OL,10,Fepidemic of knife crime.
OL,12,FMark, alongside Kiyan's mum Tracey,
OL,13,Fcontacted me at ITV News, wanting to
OL,14,Fshare memories of their "kind and
OL,15,Fthoughtful" boy.
OL,17,FThey were both deep in shock and
OL,18,Fgrief; the worst possible tragedy had
OL,19,Fengulfed their family. But they were
OL,20,Fdetermined to talk.
OL,26,@vD@YOUwD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779102176
OL,3,CDad of murdered teen Kiyan Prince is
OL,4,Ctransforming lives 20 years on
OL,6,FThey described Kiyan's cheeky sense of
OL,7,Fhumour; their pride in his emerging
OL,8,Fleadership qualities. They insisted
OL,9,FKiyan wasn't a trouble-maker. He
OL,10,Fdidn't get involved in fights. He'd
OL,11,Fstepped in to try to stop the violence.
OL,13,FMark felt passionately that young
OL,14,Fpeople were being failed. Parents
OL,15,Fcared more about buying them the right
OL,16,Ftrainers and the latest fashions, he
OL,17,Fsaid, than connecting properly with
OL,18,Ftheir kids.
OL,20,FNobody was demonstrating the
OL,21,Fdifference between right and wrong.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779102176
OL,3,CDad of murdered teen Kiyan Prince is
OL,4,Ctransforming lives 20 years on
OL,6,FHe blamed the government, too, for
OL,7,Fabdicating responsibility. Decades of
OL,8,Fclosing hundreds of youth clubs had
OL,9,Fleft teenagers with nowhere to go,
OL,10,Fnothing to do, and vulnerable to
OL,11,Fnegative influences.
OL,13,FDrugs were a huge threat; violent
OL,14,Fcrime a growing scourge.
OL,16,FSomething had to be done.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
