OL,3,CDad of murdered teen Kiyan Prince is
OL,4,Ctransforming lives 20 years on
OL,6,FMark believed sport had the power to
OL,7,Ftransform young lives. Drawing on his
OL,8,Fformer career as a professional boxer,
OL,9,Fhe started organising training
OL,10,Fsessions for local kids, to show them
OL,11,Fanother way.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FGiving them self-respect and self-
OL,19,Fcontrol. Teaching them to hold
OL,20,Fthemselves with pride - and to reject
OL,21,Fviolence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
