OL,3,CDad of murdered teen Kiyan Prince is
OL,4,Ctransforming lives 20 years on
OL,6,FAnd so the Kiyan Prince Foundation was
OL,7,Fborn.
OL,9,FExactly 20 years later I met up with
OL,10,FMark again. We'd kept in occasional
OL,11,Ftouch over the years, and I'd watched
OL,12,Fwith interest as he'd transformed his
OL,13,Fterrible loss into a force for good.
OL,15,FI took a camera crew to film one of
OL,16,Fthe after-school sessions run by the
OL,17,FFoundation, at a boxing gym in North
OL,18,FLondon. Within sight of the Tottenham
OL,19,FHotspur football ground, it's a no-
OL,20,Ffrills affair.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779102176
OL,3,CDad of murdered teen Kiyan Prince is
OL,4,Ctransforming lives 20 years on
OL,6,FMurals of famous fighters decorate the
OL,7,Fwalls; the faces Anthony Joshua and
OL,8,FTyson Fury overlooking a room packed
OL,9,Fwith youngsters; a handful of eight-
OL,10,Fyear-olds among the mostly older
OL,11,Fteens. Girls as well as boys.
OL,13,FThe training is challenging: Repeated
OL,14,Fsit-ups, star jumps, crunches.
OL,15,FSlackers are not tolerated. Poor
OL,16,Fperformance is pulled up and corrected.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779102176
OL,3,CDad of murdered teen Kiyan Prince is
OL,4,Ctransforming lives 20 years on
OL,6,FOne young lad was struggling with his
OL,7,F20 press-ups; Mark sent over an older
OL,8,Fgirl to demonstrate the right
OL,9,Ftechnique ` then everyone buckled down
OL,10,Fto tackle 20 more.
OL,12,FSupporting Mark is a team of coaches,
OL,13,Fkeeping an eye on things, and working
OL,14,Fone-on-one with less able kids.
OL,16,FSo how do they cope with such a tough
OL,17,Fregime? They seem to love it. 'Press-
OL,18,Fup boy' enthused about his improved
OL,19,Ffocus. Others talked of new-found
OL,20,Ffitness and self esteem.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779102176
OL,3,CDad of murdered teen Kiyan Prince is
OL,4,Ctransforming lives 20 years on
OL,6,FMark says there's much more still to
OL,7,Fdo. The sessions are over-subscribed.
OL,8,FToo often they have to turn kids away,
OL,9,Fbecause there's not enough room.
OL,11,FThe Foundation's new campaign - the
OL,12,FFuture Champions programme - is
OL,13,Fraising funds for a larger facility.
OL,14,FThe goal is a gym of their own, with
OL,15,FKiyan's name over the door, and
OL,16,Fcapacity for more young people.
OL,18,FMark believes every child is a
OL,19,Fpotential champion. Sport is the best
OL,20,Fway, he says, to develop a winner.
OL,21,FWhen it works "it's beautiful".
OL,26,@}D@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
