OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779102176
OL,3,CDad of murdered teen Kiyan Prince is
OL,4,Ctransforming lives 20 years on
OL,6,FThere is some cause for hope. Knife
OL,7,Fcrime is gradually falling. Official
OL,8,Ffigures for 2025 show a 10% reduction
OL,9,Fyear-on-year, and fewer young people
OL,10,Fhospitalised.
OL,12,FBut the statistics are still
OL,13,Fhorrifying. Over that same 12 months,
OL,14,F52 young people died by a knife or
OL,15,Fanother sharp implement. That's an
OL,16,Faverage of one a week.
OL,18,FMark is scathing about what he sees as
OL,19,Fthe failure of politicians to act
OL,20,Fdecisively.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779102176
OL,3,CDad of murdered teen Kiyan Prince is
OL,4,Ctransforming lives 20 years on
OL,6,F"The government are just doing what
OL,7,Fgovernments do" to look like they're
OL,8,Ftackling the issue, he says.
OL,10,F"They're not dealing with the core of
OL,11,Fthe issue. They're not focusing on the
OL,12,Fsolutions."
OL,14,FThe Home Office responds: "We are
OL,15,Fstrengthening our commitment to stop
OL,16,Fdangerous knives destroying young
OL,17,Flives ` with more than 63,000 taken
OL,18,Foff our streets under this government.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@OO]rD@AOUtD@KO]vD@[OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779102176
OL,3,CDad of murdered teen Kiyan Prince is
OL,4,Ctransforming lives 20 years on
OL,6,F"With a clear focus on education and
OL,7,Fearly intervention to tackle root
OL,8,Fcauses and a new plan to halve knife
OL,9,Fcrime, we will stop at nothing to
OL,10,Ftransform the futures of young people
OL,11,Fand protect communities."
OL,13,FHad he lived, Kiyan would now be 35
OL,14,Fyears old.
OL,16,FIn the decades since his son's murder,
OL,17,FMark's won recognition for his work,
OL,18,Fincluding several awards - among them
OL,19,Fan OBE.
OL,26,@sD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
